# Grimverse Generation Blocker

Stop generation if any of these are true:
- the shot does not resolve to a scene
- the scene does not resolve to an episode
- the shot references a character without an active state node
- the shot is marked complete but image_source or video_source is missing
- a source path is provided but the file does not exist in the vault

## Rule
Fail closed. Report the smallest safe fix. Do not guess canon. Do not auto-repair without an explicit request.

## Positive fallback
If a required file is missing, tell the user exactly which node to open and what field to correct.
